#### docsheader ####
text: Sign up with ORCID
----
ref: orcid
#### docsstep ####
step: 1
----
text: Click the orange "Sign up" button in the header.
----
image: step1.png
#### docsstep ####
step: 2
----
text: Click the "Sign up with ORCID" button.
----
image: step2-githuborcid.png

#### docsstep ####
step: 3
----
text: You will be redirected to https://orcid.org and asked to sign in.
----
image: step3-orcid.png
#### docsstep ####
step: 4
----
text: Finalise the sign up by providing your email address. A email with **confirmation instructions** is sent to the provided email address. You MUST confirm your email address in order to be able to make your first upload.
#### docstext ####
text: Congratulations you have now signed up with ORCID


