#### docsheader ####
text: Sign up with local account
----
ref: local
#### docsstep ####
step: 1
----
text: Click the orange "Sign up" button in the header.
----
image: step1.png
#### docsstep ####
step: 2
----
text: Fill in the username, full name, affiliation, email address and password. The password must be minimum 6 characters long. Finish by clicking "Sign up".
----
image: step2.png

#### docsstep ####
step: 3
----
text: If the sign up was successful, you will be redirected to the front page. A email with **confirmation instructions** is sent to the provided email address. You MUST confirm your email address in order to be able to make your first upload.


